"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-comment-expresscomment-1884634-union-flag-olympics-hate-our-country\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"What possessed the British Olympic Association to think it could \\\"rebrand\\\" the British national flag with some multicoloured nonsense that consists of squiggles, dots and vivid shades of pink and purple...?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 48, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 81, \"end\": 88, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9899492370631379, \"rank\": 0.010051030007730067, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some multicoloured nonsense\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 133}, {\"ngram\": \"squiggles\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"dots\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 166}, {\"ngram\": \"vivid shades\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 183}, {\"ngram\": \"purple\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why mess with a national flag that is instantly recognisable and respected around the world?\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Why mess\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 218}, {\"ngram\": \"a national flag\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 239}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or does the British Olympic Association think the British flag is not good enough for the British Olympic Association?\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 354, \"end\": 366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Jack\", \"score\": 0.9999996903862236, \"rank\": 3.096140314117904e-07, \"text\": \"British flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Jack\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Jack\"}, {\"begin\": 394, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Is it ashamed of our national flag and what it signifies?\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our national flag\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because if it is then it should not be called the British Olympic Association.\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am guessing they were trying to be \\\"inclusive\\\" with this pretend flag when what they were actually doing was insulting an emblem and a flag that past generations have fought and died for.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this pretend flag\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"an emblem\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"a flag\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"past generations\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyway, what kind of re-branded emblem could be better than the ACTUAL Union Jack - a flag that people in the remotest corners of the globe recognise.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996204072192455, \"rank\": 0.00027138530911357286, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what kind of re-branded emblem\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 790}, {\"ngram\": \"Jack\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"a flag\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"the remotest corners\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe recognise\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's starting to feel like certain people in certain institutions are determined to erase Britishness and stamp it out - to make it like it never existed because those people are ashamed of this country and everything it stands for.\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_national_identity\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Britishness\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_national_identity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_national_identity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"certain people\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"certain institutions\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"those people\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"this country\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These are the same people for whom patriotism equals racism.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same people\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"patriotism\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1182}, {\"ngram\": \"racism\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To them being a patriot is being a racist.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a patriot\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"a racist\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Which is ludicrous considering we live in one of the most diverse, inclusive, and tolerant countries on God's green earth.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most diverse, inclusive, and tolerant countries\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"God's green earth\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember when a string of Union Jacks were unfurled across Regent Street on Jubilee weekend in 2022 Remainiacs went into meltdown?\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1391, \"end\": 1396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9996204072192455, \"rank\": 0.00027138530911357286, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a string\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"Regent Street\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"Jubilee weekend\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"Remainiacs\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"meltdown\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hashtag #Nazi Germany was trending and India Willoughby, Britain's first trans journalist and TV newsreader, declared: \\\"When the Queen dies I would not be surprised if Boris appoints himself Fuhrer and assumes total control.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1509, \"