\"to\": 1942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What kind of mind has THAT reaction to our national flag - especially when those particular flags were to celebrate the Queen's 70 years on the throne?\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What kind\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"THAT reaction\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1979}, {\"ngram\": \"our national flag\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"those particular flags\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"the Queen's 70 years\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"the throne\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Vote on if UK should introduce a minister to protect flag after Team GB outrage Do not miss:Nigel Farage erupts at rebrand to Team GB's Union Jack Do not miss:Team GB slammed for 'insulting' decision to change Union flag to pink and purple Do not miss:Labour fury against Keir Starmer over Union Jacks on election leaflets And yes, some of those people were young.\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999920305527, \"rank\": 6.308499867968355e-09, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2173, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9003059496289925, \"rank\": 0.11072827219577029, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2202, \"end\": 2214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigel_Farage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nigel Farage\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re