ur country, only fault.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a blanket condemnation\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"no good\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2576}, {\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2591}, {\"ngram\": \"only fault\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who outrageously see the British flag as being representative of fascism.\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2630, \"end\": 2642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Jack\", \"score\": 0.9999996903862236, \"rank\": 3.096140314117904e-07, \"text\": \"British flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Jack\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Jack\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fascism\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it was to these people that the British Olympic Association was pandering to when it decided to rebrand the British flag because it thought \\\"young people\\\" would find it boring.\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2716, \"end\": 2743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2792, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Jack\", \"score\": 0.9999996903862236, \"rank\": 3.096140314117904e-07, \"text\": \"British flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Jack\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Jack\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these people\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2706}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"young people\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well tough if they do.\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Should we change everything the young find boring or do not relate to?\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because if we did there would be nothing left.\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 2996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or should we maybe expect - hope - they might try to understand what the British flag signifies to many?\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Could they perhaps try to understand those brave people who fought for this flag and died while protecting it?\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those brave people\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"this flag\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Could they try to understand what the flag means to the families of our fallen?\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the flag\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3263}, {\"ngram\": \"the families\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And could they try to understand that patriotism is not about zealotry, fascism or racism - it's about love and affection for the country you live in?\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"patriotism\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"zealotry\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3372}, {\"ngram\": \"fascism\", \"from\": 3374, \"to\": 3381}, {\"ngram\": \"racism\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3391}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"affection\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3423}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shame on The British Olympic Association for trying to jazz up the Union Jack to get the attention of the young.\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3467, \"end\": 3494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shame\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"the Union Jack\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"the attention\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3552}, {\"ngram\": \"the young\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the backlash that has resulted from its stupidity and its naivety is well deserved.\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3583}, {\"ngram\": \"its stupidity\", \"from\": 3607, \"to\": 3620}, {\"ngram\": \"its naivety\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EvenRishi Sunaksays national flags are a source of pride that really should not be messed with.\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"national flags\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3690}, {\"ngram\": \"a source\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3703}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 3707, \"to\": 3712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So now, after the backlash, the BOA is - quite rightly - back peddling.\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3785, \"end\": 3788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999893961965566, \"rank\": 9.947826424873662e-06, \"text\": \"BOA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": 